<i>adjective</i>: 훤하다 [훤ː하다], 환하다 [환ː하다], 확연하다 [화견하다], 자명하다 [자명하다], 완연하다 [와ː년하다], 역력하다 [영녀카다 ], 빤하다 [빤ː하다], 명확하다 [명화카다], 명약관화하다 [명약꽌화하다], 명백하다 [명배카다], 극명하다 [긍명하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>훤하다 [훤ː하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. bright; light</dd><br>
<dd>조금 흐릿하게 밝다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being slightly, dimly bright.</dd><br>
<dd>2. open; clear</dd><br>
<dd>앞이 탁 트여 매우 넓고 시원스럽다.</dd><br>
<dd>A view being sweeping and unobstructed.</dd><br>
<dd>3. clear; obvious</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일의 내용이나 사정이 확실하고 분명하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Something being transparent, obvious or quite predictable.</dd><br>
<dd>4. fine-looking; attractive-looking</dd><br>
<dd>외모가 잘생겨 보기에 매우 시원스럽다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having an extremely pleasing, neat, attractive appearance.</dd><br>
<dd>5. familiar; knowledgeable</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이나 대상에 대해 잘 알고 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having an accurate and deep knowledge about a certain task or object.</dd><br>
<dt>환하다 [환ː하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. bright; light; radiant</dd><br>
<dd>빛이 비치어 맑고 밝다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being very clear and bright as light shines.</dd><br>
<dd>2. open; clear</dd><br>
<dd>앞이 탁 트여 넓고 시원스럽다.</dd><br>
<dd>Something imparting a feeling of not being confined, because it has an open view.</dd><br>
<dd>3. clear; obvious</dd><br>
<dd>무슨 일이 되어 가는 사정이나 속내가 분명하다.</dd><br>
<dd>The progress or intention of a certain event being clear.</dd><br>
<dd>4. fine-looking; attractive-looking</dd><br>
<dd>얼굴이 깔끔하게 잘생겨 보기에 좋다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having a pleasing, neat, and attractive appearance.</dd><br>
<dd>5. bright; beaming; radiant</dd><br>
<dd>표정이나 성격이 명랑하고 밝다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's face or personality being bright and cheerful.</dd><br>
<dd>6. bright; light</dd><br>
<dd>색이 밝고 맑다.</dd><br>
<dd>Color being bright and clear.</dd><br>
<dd>7. familiar; knowledgeable</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이나 대상에 대해 잘 알고 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having an accurate and deep knowledge about a certain task or object.</dd><br>
<dd>8. refreshed</dd><br>
<dd>맛이 얼얼한 듯하면서 개운하고 시원한 느낌이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling tingly, clean, and refreshed in one's mouth</dd><br>
<dt>확연하다 [화견하다]</dt><br>
<dd>clear; definite; obvious; certain</dd><br>
<dd>아주 확실하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being very clear.</dd><br>
<dt>자명하다 [자명하다]</dt><br>
<dd>obvious; self-evident; self-explanatory</dd><br>
<dd>설명하거나 증명하지 않아도 저절로 알 만큼 분명하고 확실하다.</dd><br>
<dd>So clear and apparent as to be understood without any explanation or demonstration.</dd><br>
<dt>완연하다 [와ː년하다]</dt><br>
<dd>obvious; evident</dd><br>
<dd>눈에 보이는 것처럼 아주 뚜렷하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Very clear as if one could see something right before one's eyes.</dd><br>
<dt>역력하다 [영녀카다 ]</dt><br>
<dd>clear; obvious</dd><br>
<dd>감정이나 모습, 기억 등이 또렷하고 분명하다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's feelings, appearance, memory, etc., being distinct and definite.</dd><br>
<dt>빤하다 [빤ː하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. light; luminous</dd><br>
<dd>어두운 곳에 밝은 빛이 비치어 조금 환하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Slightly bright as a light shines in darkness.</dd><br>
<dd>2. obvious; palpable</dd><br>
<dd>자세히 따져 보지 않아도 될 만큼 무엇이 확실하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Something being so obvious that one does not need to think about it deeply.</dd><br>
<dd>3. fixed; steady; intent</dd><br>
<dd>바라보는 눈이 또렷하다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's staring eyes being clear.</dd><br>
<dt>명확하다 [명화카다]</dt><br>
<dd>clear; obvious</dd><br>
<dd>분명하고 확실하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Clear and sure.</dd><br>
<dt>명약관화하다 [명약꽌화하다]</dt><br>
<dd>obvious; crystal-clear</dd><br>
<dd>의심할 여지가 없이 아주 분명하고 뻔하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Absolutely clear, plain and unquestionable.</dd><br>
<dt>명백하다 [명배카다]</dt><br>
<dd>obvious; apparent; evident</dd><br>
<dd>매우 분명하고 확실하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Very clear and certain.</dd><br>
<dt>극명하다 [긍명하다]</dt><br>
<dd>definite; obvious; distinct</dd><br>
<dd>매우 분명하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Very clear.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>